obj_root_law_sections_106_content:
  string
  line `[Penalty for removing piece goods, etc., contrary to section 81.]—Omitted by The Jan`
  line `Vishwas (Amendment of Provisions) Act, 2023 (18 of 2023), s. 2 and Schedule (w.e.f. 1-8-2024).`
obj_root_law_sections_106_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_107:
  sectionId (16899)
  sectionNo (107)
  orderNo 115
  title `Penalty for falsely representing a trade mark as registered.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_107_content
  footnotes `1. Subs. by Act 18 of 2023, s. 2 and Schedule, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-8-2024)`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_11_60_00004_199947_1517807323972&sectionId=16899&sectionno=107&orderno=115&orgactid=AC_CEN_11_60_00004_199947_1517807323972
obj_root_law_sections_107_content:
  string
  line `(1) No person shall make any`
  line representation---
  line
  line `(a) with respect to a mark, not being a registered trade mark, to the effect that it is a registered`
  line `trade mark; or`
  line
  line `(b) with respect to a part of a registered trade mark, not being a part separately registered as a`
  line `trade mark, to the effect that it is separately registered as a trade mark; or`
  line
  line `(c) to the effect that a registered trade mark is registered in respect of any goods or services in`
  line `respect of which it is not in fact registered; or`
  line
  line `(d) to the effect that registration of a trade mark gives an exclusive right to the use thereof in any`
  line `circumstances in which, having regard to limitation entered on the register, the registration does not in`
  line `fact give that right.`
  line
  line `(2) If any person contravenes any of the provisions of sub-section (1), he shall be ^1[liable to penalty of`
  line `a sum equal to one half per cent. of the total sales or turnover, as the case may be, in business or of the`
  line `gross receipts in profession, as computed in the audited accounts of such person, or a sum equal to five`
  line `lakh rupees, whichever is less].`
  line
  line `(3) For the purposes of this section, the use in India in relation to a trade mark of the word`
  line `"registered", or of any other expression, symbol or sign referring whether expressly or impliedly to`
  line `registration, shall be deemed to import a reference to registration in the register, except---`
  line
  line `(a) where that word or other expression, symbol or sign is used in direct association with other`
  line `words delineated in characters at least as large as those in which that word or other expression,`
  line `symbol or sign is delineated and indicating that the reference is to registration as a trade mark under the law of a country outside India being a country under the law of which the registration referred to`
  line `is in fact in force; or`
  line
  line `(b) where that other expression, symbol or sign is of itself such as to indicate that the reference is`
  line `to such registration as is mentioned in clause (a); or`
  line
  line `(c) where that word is used in relation to a mark registered as a trade mark under the law of a`
  line `country outside India and in relation solely to goods to be exported to that country or in relation to`
  line `services for use in that country.`
obj_root_law_sections_108:
  sectionId (16900)
  sectionNo (108)
  orderNo 116
  title Omitted.
  content obj_root_law_sections_108_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_108_footnotes
